Package gaffer.data.elementdefinition

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ElementDefinition
    An ElementDefinition contains the definition for an Element type.
    ElementDefinitionWithIds
    An ElementDefinitionWithIds extends ElementDefinition and ensures element definitions also have a collection of valid identifiers.
    TypeStore
    A TypeStore simply provides a getter for getting a Type from a type name.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ElementDefinitions<EntityDef extends ElementDefinition,EdgeDef extends ElementDefinition>
    Contains the full list of groups in the graph.
    ElementDefinitions.Builder<EntityDef extends ElementDefinition,EdgeDef extends ElementDefinition>
    Builder for ElementDefinitions.
    Type
    A Type contains the an object's java class along with how to validate and aggregate the object.
    TypedEdgeDefinition
    Extends TypedElementDefinition and adds getters and setters for Edge identifiers
    TypedEdgeDefinition.Builder  
    TypedElementDefinition
    An ElementDefinition that has maps of property name to property value type and IdentifierType to identifier value type.
    TypedElementDefinition.Builder  
    TypedElementDefinitionValidator<ELEMENT_DEF extends TypedElementDefinition>  
    TypedEntityDefinition
    Extends TypedElementDefinition and adds a getter and setter for Entity vertex.
    TypedEntityDefinition.Builder  
    Types
    Types simply extends HashMap with key = String, value = Type.
